<F P=100> UKRAINE </F>
<F P=101> International Affairs </F>
<H3> <TI>   Deputy Rukh Chairman Against Nuclear Disarming </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD1101170394 Kiev UNIAN in Ukrainian 1336 GMT 11 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD1101170394 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev UNIAN </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Ukrainian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Kiev -- "I have no conclusive information about what 
was achieved by [Deputy Prime Minister] Shmarov and [Deputy 
Foreign Minister] Tarasyuk in Washington," said Oleksandr 
Lavrynovych, the deputy chairman of the People's Movement of 
Ukraine [Rukh], interviewed by a UNIAN correspondent on 11 
