period in the history of the Ukrainian People's Republic. If 
Ukraine really gives up its nuclear weapons by being promised 
some mythical compensation, and not just gives them up, but 
removes its weapons to Russian territory, it will be a step that 
will be conducive to the liquidation of Ukraine's statehood." 

