<H3> <TI>   Khabarovsk Kray `Inner Soviet' Dissolved </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD1101140994 Moscow Radio Rossii Network in Russian 1200 GMT 
11 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1101140994 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Radio Rossii Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] As of today, the activities of the Khabarovsk Kray 
inner soviet are discontinued. RIA reports that a resolution on 
this was signed by Viktor Ishayev, the head of administration of 
Khabarovsk Kray . Meanwhile, the apparatus of the dissolved 
soviet will function until 13 March. Elections to the kray's 
bodies of representative power and local self-government are to 
be held on that day. It is anticipated that specialists on the 
apparatus of the former inner soviet will help organize the 
elections and hand over documentation to the new body. 

</TEXT>

