<H3> <TI>   Khabarovsk Kray Communists Hold Plenum </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW1101082894 Khabarovsk Radio Khabarovsk Network in Russian 
0945 GMT 10 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> OW1101082894 </F>
