Language: <F P=105> French </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] One more word on the NATO summit to say that 
Vladimir Zhirinovskiy has denounced the French proposal on air 
strikes in Bosnia. In his tactful style, he described the 
proposal as being fascist. He said so in the Duma corridor 
today during the first session of the two chambers of the new 
parliament. Before it started its work, the Duma observed two 
minutes of silence in memory of the victims of the revolt of 
