<F P=100> Latvia </F>
<H3> <TI>   Delegation Leaves for Visit to Azerbaijan </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD1101195994 Riga Radio Riga Network in Latvian 1800 GMT 11 
Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1101195994 </F>
<F P=104>  Riga Radio Riga Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Latvian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] An official Latvian Government delegation, headed 
by Ojars Kehris, associate prime minister and economics 
minister, left for the Azerbaijan capital Baku today. The 
delegation includes Foreign Minister Georgs Andrejevs. 
  The delegation plans to sign protocols on establishing 
diplomatic relations between Latvia and Azerbaijan, and on trade 
and economic cooperation between the two countries in 1994. 

</TEXT>

