<F P=104>  Baku AZERTAC </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Baku, January 12 (AZERTAC)--One of the key officials 
of President Aliyev's team, 43 year old Lala Shovket Gadzhiyeva, 
M.D., who has held a position of the state secretary for the 
last half year, was given a position of permanent representative 
of Azerbaijan to the United Nations. [Baku Azerbaycan Radio 
