consider this appointment exclusion from power, as the former 
secretary of state has not been agreed with the personnel 
policy. The same analysts suppose that Minister of Foreign 
Affairs Gassan Gassanov and chairman of the National 
Independence Party of Azerbaijan Etibar Mamedov are two possible 
candidates to the state secretary vacancy. Gassan Gassanov is 
known as president's comrade-in-arms, and the national harmony 
might be the major factor dictating Etibar Mamedov's 
appointment. The state secretary position was offered to Etibar 
Mamedov last summer. 

